  "detailed_description": "<strong>Puzlogic</strong> is an unique logic puzzle game inspired by sudoku and kakuro (cross sums).<br>To complete puzzles you must drag the available numbers on the bottom to the free spaces above, following the provided rules.<br>With its minimalistic style and relaxing music, it features 64 puzzles with increasing difficulty and complexity.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/865220/extras/PL_540x405_02.gif?t=1552554623\" ><br><br><u>Features:</u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique puzzle game with familiar rules</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>64 handcrafted puzzles</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Notation on free spaces</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple drag and drop gameplay</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Ambient sounds and background effects</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Peaceful music</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Steam achievements</li></ul>",
